  <p class="small"><a href="index.html">umashankarjoshi.in</a>><a href="01.00_life.html">LIFE</a>> Chronology
    <br>
    <span class="BodyGuj"><a href="01.02_chronology-Guj.html" class="BodyGuj">ઉમાશંકર જોશી: જીવનક્રમ (ગુજરાતી)</a></span>  </p>  
  <br>
